dc_title_s: The Delaware River in the County of Camden: Showing the exterior wharf line established thereon by the Reparian Commissioners of the State of New Jersey, 1876
dc_description_s: Map covers area from Gloucester County to Burlington County. Map shows the exterior wharf line. Railroads pictured are Woodbury & Camden and Camden & Amboy. Water depths are given. Multiple properties along River are identified.
